{"tid":617611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隧道漏水　組件破損　工程安全成疑","createTime":"2018-04-05T06:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T06:42:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fcad9b346b95943ca246d0f0b5f4156bfd06db","tid":617611,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180405/20352509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352509&d=8%2BmwyUVWATMUob%2FDox0LjsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a2d69794\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352509&h=0e7cc5b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180405/20352509</a><br />\n<br />\n隧道漏水　組件破損　工程安全成疑<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180405/large/05la1p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180405%2Flarge%2F05la1p04.jpg&h=9742fa61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥（右）上月試坐高鐵「動感號」，大讚行車穩定。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】廣深港高鐵香港段由2010年動工起發生不少問題，除造價由669億元飆升至844億元及通車日期不斷延遲外，其安全性亦備受質疑。《蘋果》多次揭發工程出現問題，包括隧道漏水、預製組件破損及石屎裂痕等，惟港鐵未有理會，批准有問題的工程交予另一合約工程繼續施工，致情況惡化，恐造成安全隱患。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n列車防撞能力較低<br />\n<br />\n2016年《傳真社》揭發，由中國製造的新加坡地鐵列車出現裂紋，其中國製電池更曾在維修期間爆炸，而高鐵香港段的列車正是由同一生產商製造，質素成疑。港鐵後來解釋香港購買的列車材料有別於新加坡列車，列車也會在通車前測試以確保安全。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港鐵採購高鐵列車時又主動放棄本來沿用的歐盟防撞標準，最終購入防撞能力較低的列車，測試報告顯示列車只可抵禦時速25至30公里的撞擊，遠低於歐盟標準的36公里。有專家更質疑，廣深港高鐵有至少4種不同型號的列車營運，碰撞測試只模擬同款列車撞車情況，結果並不全面，將來通車後恐會發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳建平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t工程師：條鐵出事即條軌出事囉<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t【蘋果照相機】出軌？冇問題！<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t高鐵試車　3日出軌承托路軌工字鐵變形　叫停測試<br />\n頭條 5小時前"},{"pid":"c35aee689f07e26f93e44879ef293647b4ea9dad","tid":617611,"uid":22913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"人有多大膽 地有多大產"},{"pid":"99e40d76dadad29fd50532b6316481d28a1aac61","tid":617611,"uid":49955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"你見成班官戴哂安全帽就知中國高鐵幾危險啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dc453c93ebfd321533542781b867b2632b18ac","tid":617611,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:33:06.000Z","msg":"it is china<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631292dccc5986e0c8a02f3623cd03d18e4f0e11","tid":617611,"uid":86673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"真係幾動感刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b54fbab196e96e86bc7443a4b988fb07232767a","tid":617611,"uid":71635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"唔知班官到時夠唔夠膽坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ae54abd56284e20633514c18de5df36003da89","tid":617611,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"631292dccc5986e0c8a02f3623cd03d18e4f0e11","tid":617611,"uid":86673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"真係幾動感刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:39:39.000Z","msg":"機動遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cd995467ee528871dd61734bcbb935112c7f70","tid":617611,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"